        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued July 28 at 5:11PM PDT by NWS Pendleton OR</headline>
        <description>At 511 PM PDT, Doppler radar was tracking a strong thunderstorm near
La Pine, moving northeast at 20 mph.

HAZARD...Half inch hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Minor hail damage to vegetation is possible.

Locations impacted include...
La Pine, Three Rivers, and Sunriver.
</description>
        <instruction>If outdoors, consider seeking shelter inside a building.</instruction>
